
iOS
暫時可以用ws而不用wss，未來還是要申請wss（這樣在apple store上架才比較好過）
* https://medium.com/彼得潘的-swift-ios-app-開發問題解答集/沒有-s-的-http-還可以連線嗎-29235037e161

Info.list
1. Location
	project’s target -> info.
	(1) add ‘Privacy — Location Always Usage Description’ 
	(2) add ‘Privacy — Location Always and When In Use Usage Description’ 
	(3) add ‘Privacy — Location When In Use Usage Description’ 

2. WS/Http without SSL
	project’s target -> info.
	(1) add ‘App Transport Security Settings‘
		(1-1) add ‘Allow Arbitrary Loads‘

3. BLE
	project's target -> info
	(1) add 'Privacy — Bluetooth Peripheral Usage Description’
	(2) add ‘Privacy — Bluetooth Always Usage Description’
4. Photo library & camera
	project's target -> info
	(1) add 'Privacy - Photo Library Usage Description'
	(2) add 'Privacy - Camera Usage Description'
Reference: https://stackoverflow.com/questions/39465687/nscamerausagedescription-in-ios-10-0-runtime-crash

